title: Chorizo & Cherry Tomato Fusilli with Red Pesto & Crumbly Cheese | Serves 2
description: Got 15 quick minutes to give this lunch idea a go? Whip up a pasta salad like no other, filled to the brim with mildly spiced chunks of chorizo, a burst of sweetness from the cherry tomatoes and a rich red pesto stirred through to bring it all together. Top it off with some crumbly cheese and go for gold!
